settings.title: Frame:
settings.value: Cane-line teak: A very hard-wearing type of wood that is very suitable for outdoor use. The warm golden color creates a cozy atmosphere. A gray patina develops over time. The original color can be restored by using care oil.

settings.title: Pad:
settings.value: Cane-line AirTouch: 10% through-dyed acrylic fabric, manufactured exclusively for Cane-line. Very soft feel, at the same time robust. Easy to clean, machine washable at 30 degrees.

settings.title: braid:
settings.value: Cane-line-Soft-Rope: UV-resistant and quick-drying fiber made of woven polypropylene (PE). The velvety surface offers excellent seating comfort and can be easily cleaned with soap and water.

settings.title: Let It Flow:
settings.value: Cane-line QuickDry airflow system: Best seating comfort and highly functional at the same time. The very fast-drying interior of the upholstery consists of QuickDry-Foam, which is water-permeable, and the underside of the upholstery is open, so rainwater simply runs through the upholstery. You can quickly use your furniture again after a rain shower.

settings.title: Cane-line Angle 3 seater sofa
settings.text: The Angle Sofa impresses with its wonderful material mix of hand-picked teak and the wonderfully comfortable Cane-line Soft Rope weave in dark grey.The AirTouch cushions in elegant gray are beautifully framed by the golden-looking teak wood frame.The integrated QuickDry & AirFlow system allows rainwater to run through the upholstery, after a rain shower the upholstery is quickly dry and ready for use.A fascinating piece of furniture with the potential to become a classic.
